'''''Boesman na Lena''''' ni ikinamico ngufi yakorewe muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]] ikozwe na  Athol Fugard<ref>https://www.jstor.org/stable/441576</ref>,  Swartkops mudflats hamwe na  Port Elizabeth mur Cape town y'iburasirazuba, <ref>[http://www.encyclopedia.com/arts/educational-magazines/boesman-lena "Boesman & Lena"], Encyclopedia.com.</ref> yerekana ingaruka ya apartheid ku bantu bakeya,  hagaragaramo "umugabo n'umugore bagenda bava mu mujyi umwe bajya mu wundi<ref>https://www.supersummary.com/boesman-and-lena/summary/</ref>.

== Amavu n'amavuko ==
Mubisanzwe hamwe nibindi bikorwa byinshi bya Fugard, ikinamico yibanda ku bantu batari abazungu kandi ikubiyemo ibintu byo kwigaragambya<ref>https://www.nytimes.com/2019/02/25/theater/boesman-and-lena-review.html</ref>. ''Boesman na Lena'' batewe inkunga n'ibyabaye mu 1965 igihe Fugard yari atwaye mu umuhanda wo mu cyaro muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo<ref>https://www.supersummary.com/boesman-and-lena/summary/</ref>. Yabonye umukecuru ugenda mu muhanda izuba ryamwishe, ku bilometero uvuye aho agana, maze amuha lift. Yaratsinzwe ararira ashimira<ref>https://www.britannica.com/topic/Boesman-and-Lena</ref>. Yamubwiye ko umugabo we yari amaze gupfa kandi ko yari yagiye mu rindi sambu. iyo Fugard adahagarara, yari kurara kumuhanda<ref>https://newyorktheater.me/2019/03/02/boesman-and-lena-review-after-apartheid-fugard-turned-into-beckett/</ref>.  (Byari akamenyero muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo ivangura rishingiye]] ku gitsina abahinzi birukana imiryango y'abakozi igihe umukozi yapfaga. )<ref>https://www.enotes.com/topics/boesman</ref> Icyatangaje Fugard nuko umugore yari afite ububabare  ariko akaba ataratsinzwe. Ibi byamuteye kwandika ikinamico<ref>https://www.orlandosentinel.com/entertainment/arts-and-theater/os-et-mad-cow-boesman-lena-review-20191106-4mxlijqbtfcclntmpwnkppjhqq-story.html</ref>.

